title: Printer's Sample Book, 1880–81
creditline: Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts
description: Small notebook with handwritten formulas for dyestuffs for printed textiles. Contains 149 samples of printed fabric.

Printer's Sample Book, 1880–81.
1880–81. Medium: leather, paper, cotton. Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts. 1945-55-28.
